title: top main looking for jungle duo for cheese at the season beginning
body:
Hi,
I am top main with 500+ games as kayle and 500+ games as irelia, I peaked diamond 2 in s4 and stopped playing for 2 seasons. S7 I played casually and hit diamond, so I know the basic changes to the game from s4 to s8. 

I am searching for an equal experienced jungler, preferred MasterYi Main to push at least early season Master if not Challenger. (please have at least 1-time diamond 4 achieved)

If you like what you were reading hit me up on of my accounts:

p4per (main)
ppr smurferino 

Excuse mistakes, Englisch isn't my native language.
